    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >童话塔防是一款3D卡通风格的塔防游戏，玩法很简单，合理利用资源，建筑炮塔，然后消灭敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中每种怪物的生命值和移动速度都不尽相同，当它们拥有能量护盾时生命值将变高，南瓜炮塔对拥有能量护盾的怪物能造成额外的伤害</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特征：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6种可升级的防御炮塔</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8种怪物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >25个关卡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311220/extras/4c71c081b1452a2b329dd123505c1e81.poster.avif?t=1741584432\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311220/extras/4c71c081b1452a2b329dd123505c1e81.webm?t=1741584432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311220/extras/4c71c081b1452a2b329dd123505c1e81.mp4?t=1741584432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
